<view class="page">
  <view wx:if="{{loadError}}" class="card state-card">
    <view class="state-title">参数详情加载失败</view>
    <view class="muted">{{loadError}}</view>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
  <view class="card hero">
    <view class="device-no">{{device.deviceNo}}</view>
    <view class="title">{{device.projectName}}</view>
    <view class="device-meta">
      <view>机组型号：{{device.model}}</view>
      <view>位置/区域：{{device.area}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="viewer-tip">当前登录：{{currentUser.name}}｜{{currentUser.department}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-row">
    <view>
      <view class="section-title">电气参数知识树</view>
      <view class="muted">按类别分组，可展开/折叠；机组型号和位置作为设备基础信息展示。</view>
    </view>
    <view wx:if="{{canEdit}}" class="action-group">
      <button size="mini" class="ghost-btn" bindtap="toggleSortMode">{{sortMode ? '完成排序' : '排序'}}</button>
      <button size="mini" class="main-btn" bindtap="addParam">新增参数</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{sortMode}}" class="card sort-tip">
    <view class="muted">新增参数默认排在所有参数最后。排序时按住每行尾部“三横线”上下拖动，松手即放置；支持同分组上下拖拽排序，左右滑动手势可跨分组移动参数。</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{groupedParams.length === 0}}" class="card state-card">
    <view class="state-title">暂无参数</view>
    <view class="muted">当前设备还没有维护电气参数，可由电气设计部新增。</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:for="{{groupedParams}}" wx:key="category" class="group-card">
    <view class="group-header" data-category="{{item.category}}" bindtap="toggleGroup">
      <view>
        <view class="group-title">{{item.collapsed ? '▸' : '▾'}} {{item.category}}</view>
        <view class="muted">{{item.count}} 个参数</view>
      </view>
      <view class="group-pill">知识节点</view>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{!item.collapsed}}" class="group-body">
      <view wx:for="{{item.items}}" wx:for-item="param" wx:key="id" class="card param-card {{dragState && dragState.id === param.id ? 'dragging' : ''}}">
        <view class="param-head">
          <view class="param-name">{{param.sort}}. {{param.name}}</view>
          <view
            wx:if="{{canEdit && sortMode}}"
            class="drag-handle"
            data-id="{{param.id}}"
            data-category="{{param.category}}"
            bindtouchstart="startDrag"
            bindtouchmove="moveDrag"
            bindtouchend="endDrag"
            catchtap="endDrag"
          >
            ☰
          </view>
          <button wx:elif="{{canEdit}}" size="mini" class="edit-btn" data-id="{{param.id}}" bindtap="editParam">编辑</button>
        </view>
        <view class="param-value-block">{{param.value}} {{param.unit}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{!canEdit}}" class="card read-tip">
    <view class="muted">当前账号不是电气设计部，仅可查看参数。</view>
  </view>
  </block>
</view>
<bottom-nav />
